{
  "video_id": "sZlIgO1zLA0",
  "title": "Want a less polarised society? Try a universal basic income | Anthony Painter | TEDxExeter",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Michele Gianella Reviewer: Riaki Poništ"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9740.0,
      "end_time": 12360.0,
      "text": "So, if there was one word that you could use"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12360.0,
      "end_time": 14400.0,
      "text": "to describe current society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14400.0,
      "end_time": 15260.0,
      "text": "what might it be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17780.0,
      "text": "For me, it&#39;s the word \"polarity.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 18900.0,
      "end_time": 23370.0,
      "text": "This is the idea that people are pulling apart in politics and culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23370.0,
      "end_time": 27200.0,
      "text": "in terms of their economic opportunities, in terms of their identities."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27200.0,
      "end_time": 29710.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s deeply concerning to me. Why does it matter?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29720.0,
      "end_time": 32460.0,
      "text": "So, we&#39;ve been told that diversity is a good thing, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32460.0,
      "end_time": 35890.0,
      "text": "People from different backgrounds, perspectives, different experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35890.0,
      "end_time": 38610.0,
      "text": "coming together to solve common problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38610.0,
      "end_time": 40160.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40160.0,
      "end_time": 41650.0,
      "text": "Polarity is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41780.0,
      "end_time": 47800.0,
      "text": "Diversity is when people pull together; polarity is when people pull apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47800.0,
      "end_time": 49948.0,
      "text": "And this is one of the big challenges facing modern society."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50830.0,
      "end_time": 51870.0,
      "text": "Why is this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51870.0,
      "end_time": 53400.0,
      "text": "I think there&#39;s lots of reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53400.0,
      "end_time": 56839.0,
      "text": "but one stands out for me - it&#39;s becoming increasingly prevalent -"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56840.0,
      "end_time": 60680.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the spread of digital connecting technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60680.0,
      "end_time": 63280.0,
      "text": "And when connecting technologies spread,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63280.0,
      "end_time": 66400.0,
      "text": "they start to distribute power in different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66400.0,
      "end_time": 67720.0,
      "text": "Power, wealth, opportunity -"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67720.0,
      "end_time": 70840.0,
      "text": "it matters who you are, your skills, your luck"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70840.0,
      "end_time": 73720.0,
      "text": "and the geography you&#39;re in, the place that you live in."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73720.0,
      "end_time": 75920.0,
      "text": "And it goes in all sorts of different ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75920.0,
      "end_time": 77840.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve got to be alert to this."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77840.0,
      "end_time": 81880.0,
      "text": "And so what does it look like, this spread of connecting technologies?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81880.0,
      "end_time": 84479.0,
      "text": "Well, people are connected, which is a good thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85460.0,
      "end_time": 88809.0,
      "text": "But then power, wealth and capital start to accumulate."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90000.0,
      "end_time": 91840.0,
      "text": "Places benefit, some places:"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91840.0,
      "end_time": 93880.0,
      "text": "Millions flock to new skyscrapers;"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93880.0,
      "end_time": 97640.0,
      "text": "headquarters are built; thousands flock to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97640.0,
      "end_time": 100360.0,
      "text": "There are a huge accumulation of wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100360.0,
      "end_time": 104880.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a great swell of insecurity and precariousness alongside this."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104880.0,
      "end_time": 109660.0,
      "text": "And in fact you can see financial crashes as instability starts to increase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109660.0,
      "end_time": 112246.0,
      "text": "and then the cracks in society start to become exposed."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112246.0,
      "end_time": 113270.0,
      "text": "What happens then?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113480.0,
      "end_time": 115350.0,
      "text": "You see the rise of populist movements;"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115350.0,
      "end_time": 117699.0,
      "text": "people start to challenge the status quo."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117850.0,
      "end_time": 120770.0,
      "text": "And then we&#39;re stuck for answers: what can we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 123560.0,
      "end_time": 125320.0,
      "text": "This is the world of the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125320.0,
      "end_time": 128160.0,
      "text": "and spread of global financial capital, surely."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 128160.0,
      "end_time": 130740.0,
      "text": "But no, that&#39;s not the world I&#39;m talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131760.0,
      "end_time": 135790.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the world of the railroads in nineteenth-century America."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135790.0,
      "end_time": 138480.0,
      "text": "And we saw, then, the spread of connecting technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138480.0,
      "end_time": 140880.0,
      "text": "and the enormous impact they could have on society."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140880.0,
      "end_time": 143790.0,
      "text": "Some benefits enormously, the robber barons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143800.0,
      "end_time": 144800.0,
      "text": "in what was called the Gilded Age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144800.0,
      "end_time": 148420.0,
      "text": "and some suffered mass insecurity and inequality."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148420.0,
      "end_time": 150480.0,
      "text": "It was very similar to the current time:"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150480.0,
      "end_time": 152549.0,
      "text": "suddenly people were connected in new ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152550.0,
      "end_time": 155440.0,
      "text": "but then power was distributed in new ways as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155880.0,
      "end_time": 158190.0,
      "text": "And the simple point is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158356.0,
      "end_time": 161000.0,
      "text": "if we are not alert to what happened then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161000.0,
      "end_time": 165650.0,
      "text": "we may be doomed to replicate the mistakes of the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166130.0,
      "end_time": 169570.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m worried about one thing in particular."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169570.0,
      "end_time": 173500.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m worried most particularly about economic insecurity."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174240.0,
      "end_time": 175810.0,
      "text": "What is economic insecurity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176940.0,
      "end_time": 178880.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s when your access"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178880.0,
      "end_time": 184310.0,
      "text": "to economic opportunity, income, skills today"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 184310.0,
      "end_time": 185920.0,
      "text": "means you can&#39;t have confidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 185920.0,
      "end_time": 189700.0,
      "text": "you can maintain a standard of living and well-being in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189700.0,
      "end_time": 191579.0,
      "text": "And for too many, they can have too little confidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 191580.0,
      "end_time": 195160.0,
      "text": "they can maintain their standard of living and well-being in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 195160.0,
      "end_time": 196740.0,
      "text": "And at the Royal Society of Arts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196740.0,
      "end_time": 198940.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve been looking into this and what it means."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 198940.0,
      "end_time": 201540.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been looking at the current state of modern work."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 201540.0,
      "end_time": 204398.0,
      "text": "We were doing survey work, but we&#39;re speaking to people too."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 204660.0,
      "end_time": 208690.0,
      "text": "So take, for example, the young woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208690.0,
      "end_time": 212829.0,
      "text": "who had taken postgraduate qualifications in pharmaceuticals."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213100.0,
      "end_time": 215500.0,
      "text": "She couldn&#39;t get a job in the pharmaceutical industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215500.0,
      "end_time": 216760.0,
      "text": "so she went into retail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 216760.0,
      "end_time": 218250.0,
      "text": "temporarily, or so she thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218250.0,
      "end_time": 222410.0,
      "text": "But then she started to raise a family, and she had responsibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 222560.0,
      "end_time": 225160.0,
      "text": "Her husband had insecure income, volatile income;"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 225160.0,
      "end_time": 226340.0,
      "text": "it went up and down."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 226340.0,
      "end_time": 228470.0,
      "text": "Suddenly, she couldn&#39;t use her qualifications"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 228470.0,
      "end_time": 230930.0,
      "text": "to get into the career she wants; she became stuck."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231400.0,
      "end_time": 233829.0,
      "text": "And too many people have become stuck."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 233830.0,
      "end_time": 237840.0,
      "text": "She wants to go back and replenish her qualifications and move on up."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 237840.0,
      "end_time": 238680.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s too difficult to do so"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 238680.0,
      "end_time": 242280.0,
      "text": "because the hit on the family finances would be too great in the short term."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 242280.0,
      "end_time": 245160.0,
      "text": "This stuckness is a feature of economic insecurity."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 245160.0,
      "end_time": 248350.0,
      "text": "We discovered that only 40 percent of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248350.0,
      "end_time": 252204.0,
      "text": "think that they have good opportunities to progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 252360.0,
      "end_time": 253740.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s precarious."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 255000.0,
      "end_time": 257529.0,
      "text": "Or think about the care worker we spoke to."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 258800.0,
      "end_time": 261400.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s got a secure job; it&#39;s just low paid."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 261620.0,
      "end_time": 265800.0,
      "text": "She doesn&#39;t get paid in between visits to her patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 265800.0,
      "end_time": 270160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s extraordinarily, mentally, and physically stressful."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 270440.0,
      "end_time": 272520.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s had some training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 272520.0,
      "end_time": 275120.0,
      "text": "but she&#39;s increasingly monitored and controlled"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 275120.0,
      "end_time": 276360.0,
      "text": "in the work that she does."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 276360.0,
      "end_time": 278710.0,
      "text": "By the way, as digital technology spread,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 278710.0,
      "end_time": 281669.0,
      "text": "the opportunity for monitoring workers will become far greater."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 281670.0,
      "end_time": 283770.0,
      "text": "If you work in an Amazon distribution center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 283770.0,
      "end_time": 285340.0,
      "text": "you know exactly what this means."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 285340.0,
      "end_time": 286560.0,
      "text": "But she can&#39;t move on"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 286560.0,
      "end_time": 289150.0,
      "text": "because actually she doesn&#39;t have access to any savings"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 289150.0,
      "end_time": 290799.0,
      "text": "to change jobs and take the risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 290800.0,
      "end_time": 292820.0,
      "text": "The welfare state doesn&#39;t support her."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 293170.0,
      "end_time": 295000.0,
      "text": "If you go to the welfare state today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 295000.0,
      "end_time": 297370.0,
      "text": "you have to actually just get into a job, any job."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 297370.0,
      "end_time": 298720.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s all it cares about."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 298720.0,
      "end_time": 301600.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t care whether it&#39;s the right job or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 301600.0,
      "end_time": 304200.0,
      "text": "This is the reason that increasing numbers are going to food banks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 304200.0,
      "end_time": 306409.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s increasing on-street homelessness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 306410.0,
      "end_time": 308270.0,
      "text": "and people are increasingly precarious."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 308470.0,
      "end_time": 309780.0,
      "text": "So, she&#39;s stuck."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 310130.0,
      "end_time": 315650.0,
      "text": "And we found that 32 percent of people have access to less than £500 of savings."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 315650.0,
      "end_time": 318280.0,
      "text": "When you have access to less than £500 of savings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 318280.0,
      "end_time": 319520.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t say no."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 320000.0,
      "end_time": 322170.0,
      "text": "You have to take what&#39;s on offer to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 322200.0,
      "end_time": 327440.0,
      "text": "You are just one redundancy or a washing machine breaking down away"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 327440.0,
      "end_time": 331680.0,
      "text": "from being in a very difficult situation in terms of debt and credit."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 332130.0,
      "end_time": 336120.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not just the precarious who are facing challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 336450.0,
      "end_time": 338600.0,
      "text": "We spoke to a flexi worker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 338920.0,
      "end_time": 341240.0,
      "text": "a guy who was setting up a photography business."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 341240.0,
      "end_time": 344570.0,
      "text": "You&#39;d think he&#39;d be better off, but something went wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 344570.0,
      "end_time": 347200.0,
      "text": "He just started setting up his photography business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 347200.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately his family had a bereavement."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 349270.0,
      "end_time": 350719.0,
      "text": "And he was left in a situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 350720.0,
      "end_time": 355320.0,
      "text": "where he had to choose between his family and his business."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 355760.0,
      "end_time": 359390.0,
      "text": "No one wants to be in that position; he had nothing to fall back on."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 359360.0,
      "end_time": 362500.0,
      "text": "There was no basic foundation on which he could make decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 362500.0,
      "end_time": 367420.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re seeing a spread of economic insecurity all around."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 368265.0,
      "end_time": 369354.0,
      "text": "The big risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 370490.0,
      "end_time": 374110.0,
      "text": "is that this state will become persistent"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 374110.0,
      "end_time": 377560.0,
      "text": "as digital connecting technologies spread."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 377910.0,
      "end_time": 379780.0,
      "text": "We know digital connecting technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 379780.0,
      "end_time": 384890.0,
      "text": "can create enormous accumulations of wealth and power."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 385690.0,
      "end_time": 387240.0,
      "text": "And just last week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 387194.0,
      "end_time": 389490.0,
      "text": "we had Mark Zuckerberg, the founder of Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 389490.0,
      "end_time": 390810.0,
      "text": "appearing before Congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 390810.0,
      "end_time": 393210.0,
      "text": "And he described Facebook as a series of tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 393500.0,
      "end_time": 395270.0,
      "text": "which sounds pretty benign."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 395530.0,
      "end_time": 397390.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s far more than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 397610.0,
      "end_time": 401630.0,
      "text": "It actually is a way of distributing power and relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 401630.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "and access to jobs, income, wealth, in vastly different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 406450.0,
      "end_time": 408550.0,
      "text": "Increasingly, digital connecting technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 408550.0,
      "end_time": 410230.0,
      "text": "are becoming tapestry of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 410230.0,
      "end_time": 412000.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re woven into our personalities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 412000.0,
      "end_time": 415750.0,
      "text": "our personal, economic, political relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 415780.0,
      "end_time": 422229.0,
      "text": "So the warning signs are there, but we know it can be different."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 423330.0,
      "end_time": 424450.0,
      "text": "How do we know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 425260.0,
      "end_time": 428240.0,
      "text": "We know because we&#39;ve taken this on before."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 431190.0,
      "text": "In the Gilded Age that I described in 19th century America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 431190.0,
      "end_time": 432460.0,
      "text": "in the early 20th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 432460.0,
      "end_time": 437719.0,
      "text": "a group of visionary journalists, writers, activists, trade unionists, politicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 437720.0,
      "end_time": 439250.0,
      "text": "started to campaign against it."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 439250.0,
      "end_time": 441970.0,
      "text": "Visionary presidents started to use the power of the state"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 441970.0,
      "end_time": 443260.0,
      "text": "to take on economic power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 443470.0,
      "end_time": 446560.0,
      "text": "to put resource and income in the hands of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 446560.0,
      "end_time": 448500.0,
      "text": "to put in fair taxation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 448500.0,
      "end_time": 450780.0,
      "text": "and started to reverse the polarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 451502.0,
      "end_time": 453680.0,
      "text": "We need to learn from that today."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 453680.0,
      "end_time": 456400.0,
      "text": "And the picture of the current world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 456400.0,
      "end_time": 459880.0,
      "text": "as we go into a wider spread of digital technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 459880.0,
      "end_time": 461120.0,
      "text": "is one of polarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 461560.0,
      "end_time": 464750.0,
      "text": "The wealthiest 10 percent earn half of the wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 465420.0,
      "end_time": 469360.0,
      "text": "The bottom have access to less than £500 of savings."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 469770.0,
      "end_time": 474440.0,
      "text": "And only 40 percent of people have good opportunities to progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 474340.0,
      "end_time": 478599.0,
      "text": "This is what a polarized society looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 478600.0,
      "end_time": 480150.0,
      "text": "But we know it can be different."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 480150.0,
      "end_time": 483560.0,
      "text": "This is a time for ideas, for big ideas and action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 483560.0,
      "end_time": 485770.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to share one idea with you today."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 485770.0,
      "end_time": 487490.0,
      "text": "One idea is not enough, by the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 488410.0,
      "end_time": 492900.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m going to share with you the idea of the universal basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 492240.0,
      "end_time": 494830.0,
      "text": "Universal basic income is a really simple concept."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 494830.0,
      "end_time": 497599.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s giving everyone access to a small amount of resource"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 497600.0,
      "end_time": 500380.0,
      "text": "so that they have a base level of security as of right."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 500600.0,
      "end_time": 502660.0,
      "text": "Everyone gets it, it&#39;s unconditional."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 502870.0,
      "end_time": 504200.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s universal."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 504840.0,
      "end_time": 506599.0,
      "text": "So you have that bedrock of security"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 506600.0,
      "end_time": 510680.0,
      "text": "on which yuu make better decisions to learn, earn, set up a business, care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 510680.0,
      "end_time": 511630.0,
      "text": "whatever it may be."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 511630.0,
      "end_time": 513120.0,
      "text": "Now, will this work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 513990.0,
      "end_time": 515640.0,
      "text": "The answer is emphatically yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 515659.0,
      "end_time": 516929.0,
      "text": "How do I know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 517400.0,
      "end_time": 519690.0,
      "text": "I know because it&#39;s been tried."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 519169.0,
      "end_time": 520419.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been tried in Alaska."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 520740.0,
      "end_time": 523799.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve had a basic-income-style payment for the last 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 523799.0,
      "end_time": 527130.0,
      "text": "The critics say, about basic income, \"People get lazy. It won&#39;t work.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 527130.0,
      "end_time": 528610.0,
      "text": "No evidence for that in Alaska."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 528640.0,
      "end_time": 529830.0,
      "text": "People carry on working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 529830.0,
      "end_time": 532220.0,
      "text": "but they manage their household finances better."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 532220.0,
      "end_time": 533940.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been tried in India and Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 534480.0,
      "end_time": 536300.0,
      "text": "And rather than social collapse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 536300.0,
      "end_time": 538300.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s led to a spread of entrepreneurialism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 538300.0,
      "end_time": 540800.0,
      "text": "of civic activity, of women leaving the home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 540800.0,
      "end_time": 542300.0,
      "text": "of greater equality."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 542300.0,
      "end_time": 543920.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been tried in North Carolina."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 543920.0,
      "end_time": 544930.0,
      "text": "The critics said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 544930.0,
      "end_time": 548300.0,
      "text": "\"Basic income? Well, people will just sit back, kick back."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 548310.0,
      "end_time": 551310.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll drink more, take drugs, have a good time, whatever.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 551310.0,
      "end_time": 554839.0,
      "text": "The evidence? Drug addiction and alcohol addiction went down."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 554840.0,
      "end_time": 556110.0,
      "text": "Mental health improved."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 556150.0,
      "end_time": 557840.0,
      "text": "Health outcomes are improved."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 557840.0,
      "end_time": 560250.0,
      "text": "Educational outcomes are improved."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 560250.0,
      "end_time": 562420.0,
      "text": "Wherever it has been tried, it has worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 562420.0,
      "end_time": 566800.0,
      "text": "The same happened when it was tried in the province of Manitoba in Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 566800.0,
      "end_time": 568880.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s now being tried in Finland."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 568880.0,
      "end_time": 571330.0,
      "text": "So we know wherever it has been tried,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 571330.0,
      "end_time": 572488.0,
      "text": "it has worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 572620.0,
      "end_time": 575800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a big step to a universal basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 575340.0,
      "end_time": 578280.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s things that we can do now to move toward it."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 578280.0,
      "end_time": 579949.0,
      "text": "At the Royal Society of Arts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 579950.0,
      "end_time": 583420.0,
      "text": "we have proposed what we are calling a Universal Basic Opportunity Fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 583420.0,
      "end_time": 585660.0,
      "text": "which is something that we can do right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 585660.0,
      "end_time": 589449.0,
      "text": "And the idea here is that we would give a fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 589450.0,
      "end_time": 593300.0,
      "text": "a 200-billion-pound endowment from government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 593300.0,
      "end_time": 596699.0,
      "text": "borrowing, using the low interest rates available to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 596730.0,
      "end_time": 598830.0,
      "text": "and with that endowment, we would invest:"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 599160.0,
      "end_time": 601699.0,
      "text": "invest in our economic and social future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 601940.0,
      "end_time": 606290.0,
      "text": "and invest in digital, transport, housing, energy infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 606920.0,
      "end_time": 609175.0,
      "text": "And when those investments delivered a return,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 609779.0,
      "end_time": 611730.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d then make payments to people"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 611730.0,
      "end_time": 614100.0,
      "text": "so they could have two years of basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 614100.0,
      "end_time": 616450.0,
      "text": "to make different decisions about their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 617300.0,
      "end_time": 618930.0,
      "text": "So they could invest in their training."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 618930.0,
      "end_time": 620989.0,
      "text": "They could assume care and responsibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 620990.0,
      "end_time": 622840.0,
      "text": "They could try a new business."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 622840.0,
      "end_time": 625400.0,
      "text": "They could change their work if they wanted to."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 625400.0,
      "end_time": 629630.0,
      "text": "This could be an enormous step up, a helping hand rather than the slap-down"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 629630.0,
      "end_time": 632400.0,
      "text": "that the current welfare state too often delivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 632260.0,
      "end_time": 634730.0,
      "text": "And how would we replenish this fund over time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 634990.0,
      "end_time": 638244.0,
      "text": "Well, we&#39;d look at those high flyers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 638453.0,
      "end_time": 641260.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;d say, \"You could make a bit more of a contribution.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 641260.0,
      "end_time": 644470.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d look at some of the digital platforms and we could, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 644480.0,
      "end_time": 647350.0,
      "text": "levy the data that we provide to those big digital platforms."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 647350.0,
      "end_time": 649540.0,
      "text": "Some people have called this a \"Facebook Levy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 649900.0,
      "end_time": 651459.0,
      "text": "And we would look for corporates"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 651460.0,
      "end_time": 654720.0,
      "text": "who have had a 20-billion-pound tax break in the last 10 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 654720.0,
      "end_time": 656410.0,
      "text": "to make a contribution as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 656410.0,
      "end_time": 658699.0,
      "text": "Then this fund becomes sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 659160.0,
      "end_time": 661319.0,
      "text": "But this is a step that we can make today."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 661320.0,
      "end_time": 662870.0,
      "text": "Does this sort of fund work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 663000.0,
      "end_time": 664000.0,
      "text": "Well, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 664320.0,
      "end_time": 665770.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve tried it in Norway."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 665770.0,
      "end_time": 668939.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s delivered a return and invested in public infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 668940.0,
      "end_time": 671750.0,
      "text": "it invested in the social infrastructure, on the back of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 671750.0,
      "end_time": 674190.0,
      "text": "We can do it here, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 674940.0,
      "end_time": 676720.0,
      "text": "The payments are made from this fund."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 676720.0,
      "end_time": 679450.0,
      "text": "The basic opportunity dividend can make all the difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 679450.0,
      "end_time": 681310.0,
      "text": "to that retail worker I talked about."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 681310.0,
      "end_time": 683589.0,
      "text": "It can enable her to step away for a year or two"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 683590.0,
      "end_time": 686540.0,
      "text": "to replenish her qualifications and improve her opportunities."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 686540.0,
      "end_time": 689189.0,
      "text": "To the care worker who&#39;s at risk of being monitored"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 689190.0,
      "end_time": 692260.0,
      "text": "and is stuck and can&#39;t make a different decision to change work -"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 692260.0,
      "end_time": 695189.0,
      "text": "even though her job is secure, she&#39;s not economically secure -"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 695190.0,
      "end_time": 696810.0,
      "text": "she could make a different choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 696810.0,
      "end_time": 698930.0,
      "text": "The flexi worker setting up a new business"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 698930.0,
      "end_time": 701900.0,
      "text": "could have had a better platform or foundation for his business"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 701900.0,
      "end_time": 702900.0,
      "text": "as he went forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 702900.0,
      "end_time": 706150.0,
      "text": "They wouldn&#39;t have had to choose between his family and his business."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 706150.0,
      "end_time": 709120.0,
      "text": "The high flyer, well, they may have to contribute more."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 709120.0,
      "end_time": 710160.0,
      "text": "But you know what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 710740.0,
      "end_time": 712100.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a small price to pay"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 712100.0,
      "end_time": 716180.0,
      "text": "for a society that is more economically and socially stable."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 716700.0,
      "end_time": 719560.0,
      "text": "These are things that we can do today."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 719990.0,
      "end_time": 722310.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have to accept polarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 722310.0,
      "end_time": 726250.0,
      "text": "We know from history what happens if we don&#39;t act."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 726250.0,
      "end_time": 728800.0,
      "text": "We can reverse polarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 728800.0,
      "end_time": 730910.0,
      "text": "We can think of new ways of connecting."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 730910.0,
      "end_time": 733250.0,
      "text": "We can invest in people in different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 733250.0,
      "end_time": 735440.0,
      "text": "And there are cities across the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 735440.0,
      "end_time": 738360.0,
      "text": "that are volunteering to have basic income experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 738360.0,
      "end_time": 740430.0,
      "text": "because they know it can make a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 740430.0,
      "end_time": 741959.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s some in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 741970.0,
      "end_time": 744900.0,
      "text": "North Ayrshire, Fife, Edinburgh and Glasgow"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 744120.0,
      "end_time": 746360.0,
      "text": "all want to have basic income experiments."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 746360.0,
      "end_time": 749360.0,
      "text": "The Scottish government is supporting them and exploring that."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 749360.0,
      "end_time": 753620.0,
      "text": "In Finland, in Barcelona, in the Netherlands, in Canada,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 753640.0,
      "end_time": 756720.0,
      "text": "in Stockton and Oakland in California, in India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 756720.0,
      "end_time": 760460.0,
      "text": "there is a movement behind trying this because people believe it can be better."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 760460.0,
      "end_time": 763170.0,
      "text": "We can give people a more secure footing."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 763170.0,
      "end_time": 767360.0,
      "text": "Greater Exeter could volunteer to host a basic income pilot here too."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 767360.0,
      "end_time": 769580.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a sort of action you can take to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 769580.0,
      "end_time": 772370.0,
      "text": "\"We want to do things differently here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 773280.0,
      "end_time": 775200.0,
      "text": "We can do the things differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 775200.0,
      "end_time": 777600.0,
      "text": "We can look at the past and learn from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 777600.0,
      "end_time": 778610.0,
      "text": "We can act now."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 778610.0,
      "end_time": 782160.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s not wait the decades it took after 19th century to act."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 782160.0,
      "end_time": 784199.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s learn from that and let&#39;s do it now."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 784200.0,
      "end_time": 786840.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s put more power back in people&#39;s hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 787150.0,
      "end_time": 788863.0,
      "text": "And let&#39;s cultivate a society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 789122.0,
      "end_time": 794360.0,
      "text": "a society where opportunity, creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 794579.0,
      "end_time": 798423.0,
      "text": "security, freedom are shared."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 799710.0,
      "end_time": 802290.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}